item.title: F2P style servers out
item.dc:creator: @davidi2 Davidi2
item.description:
@davidi2 wrote:

[quote=“Acorn_, post:14, topic:518846”]Oh yeah, I guess I forgot how much money they spent with all that fast money they made that triples, if not quadruples times a thousand how much they spend on a single server.
Don’t have the same pull david? is that right? Is that why the amount of players on both games are almost equal, if not 07 being greater? Is that why the demand for 07 gold is 100k:10m?
Please…[/quote]You seriously have no idea what you’re talking about. The pull is about PULL TO PAY FOR MEMBERSHIP, not pull to play. It has nothing at all to do with ‘players online’. The reason f2p exists on the normal game is to be a trial, to try and get people to pay for membership. OSR is targeted at people that have already played the game before. So if you’ve played the game before and know you don’t want to pay for membership, they have no reason to spend extra money to give you a free trial for no money back.
